Title: A Bullet Runs Through It (1)
Plot: The team investigates the death of a police officer who died during a shootout, leaving hundreds of bullets on the crime scene. Sofia wonders if it was her who fired the fatal shot.
ParentalRatingReason: Violence and content that may disturb
